    <item>
      <title>瑞士监管机构加大对瑞士宝盛银行 Benko 业务的打击力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/swiss-regulator-opens-proceedings-against-julius-baer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士金融监管机构 Finma 表示，已对瑞士宝盛集团有限公司 (Julius Baer Group Ltd.) 启动执法程序，加大对该银行与 Signa 房地产帝国崩溃相关的风险违约的打击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/swiss-regulator-opens-proceedings-against-julius-baer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 12:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税威胁供应，美国石油涨幅超过全球油价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-oil-gains-outpace-global-benchmark-on-trump-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布征收关税，威胁到美国两大外国供应国的石油供应后，美国原油基准价格的涨幅超过其他石油市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-oil-gains-outpace-global-benchmark-on-trump-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税措施后投资者纷纷涌向美元避险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/wall-street-backs-the-dollar-s-wild-rally-to-gather-steam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团和摩根大通等华尔街银行认为，即使在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税举措导致美元飙升之后，购买美元仍然可以赚到很多钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/wall-street-backs-the-dollar-s-wild-rally-to-gather-steam</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元兑美元逆转跌势，展现避险吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/yen-shows-glimpses-of-haven-appeal-even-as-dollar-pushes-it-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普征收新关税后，日元周一抵御住了美元的冲击，表明投资者仍然认为日元在动荡时期具有避风港的价值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/yen-shows-glimpses-of-haven-appeal-even-as-dollar-pushes-it-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:29:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税导致美元上涨、股指期货下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国开始征收关税并引发威胁全球经济增长的贸易战，美元飙升，股市暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普瞄准漏洞 Temu，Shein 曾与亚马逊较量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收的新贸易税包括对国际电子商务的猛烈攻击，显然是计划取消长期以来对价值低于 800 美元的包裹的关税豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 04:15:36 GMT</pubDate>
